<div class='post_block hentry clear clearfix  ' id='post_id_1409015'>
		<a id='entry1409015'></a>
		
	
		
		<div class='post_wrap' >
			
				<h3 class='row2'>
			
				<span class='post_id right ipsType_small desc blend_links'>
					
						<a itemprop="replyToUrl" data-entry-pid='1409015' href='http://forums.phpfreaks.com/topic/273788-designing-a-social-network-not-sure-on-a-couple-of-points/#entry1409015' rel='bookmark' title='designing a social network - not sure on a couple of points: post #5'>
					
					#5
					<img src='http://forums.phpfreaks.com/public/style_images/phpfreaks/icon_share.png' class='small' title='designing a social network - not sure on a couple of points: post #5' />
					</a>
